title: PEACH UPSIDE DOWN CAKE
directions: Melt butter in 13 x 9 x 2 inch pan. Sprinkle brown sugar in pan and stir until it caramelizes. Place peaches on caramel mixture. Mix cake as directed and pour over peaches. Bake at 350 degrees 45 to 50 minutes until cake tests done with toothpick. Let stand 5 minutes to set, then turn upside down on a large dish.
ingredients: 1 pkg. Duncan Hines yellow deluxe cake mix
